      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint retains a nice luster, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only minimal wear visible on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Mechanically, the engine and transmission run smoothly, and all onboard electronics are fully functional. This is a solid, reliable car that offers a great balance of quality and value for its next owner.",
