    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and still feels great on the road. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more adventures. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that's ready to go today, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This specimen features a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory-spec variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The engine exhibits excellent compression across all cylinders, and the valve clearances have been recently shimmed to factory specifications. While the exterior shows honest signs of road use, the drivetrain remains tight with precise throttle response from the individual throttle bodies. It sits on a refreshed suspension with upgraded bushings, providing the tactile feedback and damping characteristics expected of a true driver's car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance history. Clean title. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and value, having been maintained with a high level of care. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, showing only the minor, superficial character marks one would expect from a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the seats are supportive and free of significant wear, and the climate control blows ice-cold. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has benefited from regular, documented oil changes. All electronic features, from the infotainment system to the power windows, are fully operational. It drives straight and true, with firm braking and a quiet suspension. This is an ideal choice for someone seeking a dependable, attractive vehicle that looks and feels much younger than its mileage suggests.",
      "price": 33850.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies the intersection of performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure all mechanical systems meet our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and longevity. With a clean service history and an interior that reflects careful stewardship, this vehicle offers a superior driving experience and exceptional long-term value for the sophisticated buyer.",
      "price": 34800.0,
