    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I'm parting with my car and it's in really lovely shape! It\u2019s been well-maintained and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips. It\u2019s got a lot of life left in it and I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
