    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for superior power delivery. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and a responsive steering rack, providing the communicative feedback and balanced weight distribution synonymous with the marque. A well-sorted, driver-focused machine ready for immediate engagement.",
